a couple of days.

00:09:09.956 --> 00:09:12.286 A:middle
I'm going to go for
an outdoor run again

00:09:12.286 --> 00:09:14.146 A:middle
because I always run outside.

00:09:14.696 --> 00:09:16.086 A:middle
When I launch the Fitness app,

00:09:16.166 --> 00:09:18.716 A:middle
