00:09:40.856 --> 00:09:43.946 A:middle
It's unlikely for me
to change this setting.

00:09:44.716 --> 00:09:46.446 A:middle
By displaying it by
default, I don't have

00:09:46.486 --> 00:09:49.006 A:middle
to swipe past three screens
every single time I want

00:09:49.006 --> 00:09:51.216 A:middle
to go for a run.

00:09:51.216 --> 00:09:54.836 A:middle
By remembering basic
