suit my individual preferences.



00:09:58.146 --> 00:10:01.506 A:middle
Fitness is tailoring itself to
suit my individual preferences.

00:10:02.526 --> 00:10:05.166 A:middle
There's no configuration
that happens per se.

00:10:05.556 --> 00:10:06.976 A:middle
It just happens automatically.

00:10:06.976 --> 00:10:10.476 A:middle
It is a bit like having a
