00:24:37.106 --> 00:24:39.896 A:middle
[Tone] That has a nice
ring to it, right?

00:24:40.396 --> 00:24:41.146 A:middle
Very positive.

00:24:41.816 --> 00:24:43.016 A:middle
In context.

00:24:43.746 --> 00:24:48.446 A:middle
[Tone] So this tone
is really good

00:24:48.686 --> 00:24:50.566 A:middle
for providing people
positive feedback

00:24:51.126 --> 00:24:53.346 A:middle
like they are taking a quiz
