00:26:05.886 --> 00:26:08.606 A:middle
Finally there's a special

00:26:08.776 --> 00:26:11.646 A:middle
and subtle haptic
called a click haptic.

00:26:12.376 --> 00:26:14.966 A:middle
This one as I said
is a bit special.

00:26:15.066 --> 00:26:17.786 A:middle
As you can see it's far
