00:26:38.686 --> 00:26:42.386 A:middle
This haptic provides the
sensation of a dial clicking

00:26:42.786 --> 00:26:45.986 A:middle
at predefined increments
or intervals.

00:26:46.526 --> 00:26:50.776 A:middle
[Clicking sound] This haptic is
good for things like this dial.

00:26:56.256 --> 00:26:58.686 A:middle
[Clicking sound]
Now, if you notice,

00:26:58.686 --> 00:27:01.676 A:middle
this dial has minor tick
marks and major tick marks.



00:26:58.686 --> 00:27:01.676 A:middle
