00:47:39.766 --> 00:47:42.646 A:middle
You can modify those with
fine grained controls

00:47:42.646 --> 00:47:46.046 A:middle
for noise reduction,
speech attenuation

00:47:46.366 --> 00:47:47.716 A:middle
and wind cancellation.

00:47:48.586 --> 00:47:51.706 A:middle
Now each of these settings
